title: to those afraid of change
pid: 28a2b17e-80dd-4240-a641-87b48a0b04ce
body: |2-
  There is one truth.
  One total flavor of our somewhat-contradictory
    diversity of beliefs, preferences, memories, ideas.
  One quantum gestalt of human knowing.
  To know it is to rob change, even death, of their sting.

  Sharing a knowledge graph is the best we can do
  to pin down that quantum gestalt.
